OL,5, Facial recognition firm Clearview has  
OL,6, run nearly a million searches for US   
OL,7, police, its founder has told the BBC   
OL,9,FCEO Hoan Ton-That also revealed        
OL,10,FClearview now has 30bn images scraped  
OL,11,Ffrom platforms such as Facebook, taken 
OL,12,Fwithout users' permissions.            
OL,14,FThe company has been repeatedly fined  
OL,15,Fmillions of dollars in Europe and      
OL,16,FAustralia for breaches of privacy.     
OL,18,FCritics argue that the police's use of 
OL,19,FClearview puts everyone into a         
OL,20,F"perpetual police line-up".            
